rows.label: bf05470100_0030
rows.name: Invidian army! So many of them!

rows.label: bf05470100_0070
rows.name:
This is terrible. 
At this rate, both armies will engage in battle.

rows.label: bf05470100_0110
rows.name:
This is bad. If someone doesn't
explain what's really going on...

rows.label: bf05470100_0120
rows.name: But we won't make it in time now.

rows.label: bf05470100_0130
rows.name:
What are we going to do? 
Isn't there any way?

rows.label: bf05470100_0140
rows.name: Dora cannons. They're Invidia's main weapons.

rows.label: bf05470100_0150
rows.name:
On this side too. Superbia's army has also begun
preparations for bombardment, meh.

rows.label: bf05470100_0160
rows.name: It doesn't matter whether we make it in time or not.

rows.label: bf05470100_0170
rows.name: We need to get to Invidia!
